                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160110-93-off520 t18160110-93-cd522"></join>, with intent to steal, and for burglariously stealing therein, a sack, value 2s. the goods of Elizabeth Spenser; eighteen tame pigeons, value 30s. and a guinea-pig, value 1s.
